{"tid":1670761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"乜乜乜冇人講，呢排成日見到呢句","createTime":"2019-10-23T06:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T07:25:31.000Z","uid":48234,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b55184854124e51a55dfb2c49ccda3550d2a6297","tid":1670761,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:08:06.000Z","msg":"呢排香港發生太多事<br />\n而且好多單都係大事<br />\n有人就想集中睇下次行動資訊<br />\n有人想回顧6月9號以來全部香港大事<br />\n有人想搵返全部失蹤手足<br />\n<br />\n但係香港人能力始終有限<br />\n香港人始終唔係「全能的神」<br />\n需要放鬆就放鬆，有能力就繼續爭取<br />\n做你能力範圍內做到嘅事<br />\n檢討定期做一次，唔好隨便分化割蓆<br />\n<br />\n反送中大事紀，賤賊濫暴紀錄，我知道有巴/絲打整理緊，最好宣傳多啲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n祝赤納粹早日解體</span></span>"},{"pid":"79297904ef7e36bed7a7e1cd87663dd2c7a429f3","tid":1670761,"uid":55973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:23:12.000Z","msg":"個個都想用依類標題推起個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6211768314e79aabfeb6f785c91a6bc55ab26844","tid":1670761,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79297904ef7e36bed7a7e1cd87663dd2c7a429f3","tid":1670761,"uid":55973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:23:12.000Z","msg":"個個都想用依類標題推起個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T07:16:58.000Z","msg":"但係咁撚多post又點推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1547d54812f204ef81b7f0aa281fd2ec33de46a","tid":1670761,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T07:25:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}